$(function(){const t=$("#jsCustomSelect"),e=$(".selectDefaultBox");$(".selectContainer").on("click",".optionContainer",function(){const n=$(this).text().trim().toLowerCase();t.children().filter(function(o,i){$(i).text().trim().toLowerCase().indexOf(n)>=0&&(t.children().eq(o).prop("selected",!0),e.text($(i).text()))})})});